47
00:03:30.660 --> 00:03:33.500
He's got a massive beard
and heaps of tatts.

48
00:03:41.220 --> 00:03:43.580
They're going to
stink that cell out.

49
00:03:43.660 --> 00:03:44.460
The boys are on ice

50
