68
00:04:20.020 --> 00:04:21.820
That's still a lot
of bush. Brett.

69
00:04:21.900 --> 00:04:23.780
Well. what can we do now?

70
00:04:23.860 --> 00:04:25.860
Move the search
team to Timbertop

71
00:04:25.940 --> 00:04:27.700
