Just on Clinker.

81
00:05:41.980 --> 00:05:44.140
Clinker! What the
hell's Clinker?

82
00:05:44.220 --> 00:05:45.060
It's an app.

83
00:05:45.100 --> 00:05:48.420
He's High Elf
Gringleback. I'm Borg 364.

84
00:05:55.700 --> 00:05:57.820
- Heya.
- Hey.

85
00:05:58.580 --> 00:05:59.996
What a weekend. I am exhausted.

86
00:06:00.020 --> 00:06:01.260
What a weekend. I am exhausted.

87
00:06:01.620 --> 00:06:04.860
- I got hit by a car.
- You what?

88
00:06:05.300 --> 00:06:07.460
Yeah. long story short.

89
00:06:07.540 --> 00:06:09.020
I spent the night
up on the mountain.

90
00:06:09.060 --> 00:06:11.180
