222
00:17:20.180 --> 00:17:22.220
Just trust me. okay?

223
00:17:22.300 --> 00:17:27.100
Listen. I'm going to be right
here. okay? Not far away.

224
00:17:27.380 --> 00:17:29.060
I won't let anything
bad happen to you.

225
00:17:29.700 --> 00:17:31.700
