Deputy. Kayden.

226
00:17:31.780 --> 00:17:33.300
That's a very
important position.

227
00:17:33.380 --> 00:17:35.300
How much does the
Deputy get paid?

228
00:17:40.980 --> 00:17:42.380
There you go.

229
00:17:52.180 --> 00:17:53.780
You're a charger!

230
00:17:57.380 --> 00:17:59.996
Kay. stay where I can see you.

231
00:18:00.020 --> 00:18:00.340
Kay. stay where I can see you.

232
00:18:00.420 --> 00:18:02.540
Okay.

233
00:18:29.020 --> 00:18:30.500
We've closed off the road.

234
00:18:31.180 --> 00:18:32.500
